```sql
-- int_deduped_returns.sql
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        item_id,
        return_date,
        reason,
        status,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY item_id
            ORDER BY
                CASE WHEN status = 'approved' THEN 0 ELSE 1 END,
                return_date DESC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_returns') }}
)
SELECT
    item_id,
    return_date,
    reason,
    status
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1
```

-- fct_return_rates_by_category.sql
WITH items_with_category AS (
    SELECT
        oi.item_id,
        oi.quantity,
        COALESCE(c.category_name, '(unknown)') AS category_name
    FROM {{ ref('stg_order_items') }} oi
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_products') }} p
        ON p.product_id = oi.product_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_categories') }} c
        ON c.category_id = p.category_id
)
SELECT
    i.category_name,
    SUM(i.quantity) AS total_items_sold,
    COALESCE(SUM(r.returned_quantity), 0) AS total_items_returned,
    COALESCE(SUM(r.returned_quantity), 0) * 1.0 / SUM(i.quantity) AS return_rate
FROM items_with_category i
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT
        dr.item_id,
        1 AS returned_quantity
    FROM {{ ref('int_deduped_returns') }} dr
) r
    ON r.item_id = i.item_id
GROUP BY
    i.category_name
ORDER BY
    return_rate DESC
